#
#       Neighbourhood Algorithm input options file
#
0        : Algorithm type (NA or Uniform MC: 1=MC,0=NA)
70        : Maximum number of iterations
30        : Sample size for first iteration
30        : Sample size for all other iterations
7        : Number of cells to re-sample 
y,210728  : Use Quasi random number generator ? (y/n);random seed 
0         : Type of initial sample (0=random;1=read in a NAD file)
2         : Output information level (0=silent,1=summary info,2=1+models)
y         : Turn timing mode on ? (y/n)
n         : Turn debug mode on ? (y/n)
